Description
Get full control of your bet tickets anytime and anywhere
Get full control of your bet tickets anytime and anywhere.
The Bet Tracker App offers a broad range of industry-leading betting management options, giving you full control of your bets.
Check your tickets status anytime on-the-go, watch the live match flow to follow in-play events in real time or cash out early if your bet turns against you.
You can also transfer won tickets back to a terminal in a shop!
