Seems badly developed
Tapping on the bottom tabs opens diferent views. But tapping on the same tab multiple times adds adds views where all are the same. Using the swipe gesture on iphone is enabled and doing so you can see how many times you've opened that page because you can keep swiping through them this way.
Simple if check to see if you are already on that view would have fixed that.
Poor effort
