Major Fault with slow resolution
On a couple of occasions this App has wiped all my bets, including winning ones. Getting a resolution is slow and tedious. Boylesports have to call BGT and wait for them to call back, I’ve been waiting 3 days for my current issue to be resolved.
I would avoid this App until this is sorted.
